```markdown
# Movie Recommendation System

This is a simple movie recommendation system implemented in Python. Given a movie description, the system suggests the title of the most similar movie from a list of movies.

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- spaCy (Install using `pip install spacy`)
- spaCy English language model (Download using `python -m spacy download en_core_web_md`)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```
   git clone <repository_url>
   ```

2. Navigate to the project directory:

   ```
   cd movie-recommendation-system
   ```

3. Install the required dependencies:

   ```
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

4. Prepare the movie data:
   - Open the `movies.txt` file.
   - Update the file with your movie descriptions in the following format:

     ```
     Movie A :When Hiccup discovers Toothless isn't the only Night Fury, he must seek "The Hidden World", a secret Dragon Utopia before a hired tyrant named Grimmel finds it first.
     Movie B :After the death of Superman, several new people present themselves as possible successors.
     Movie C :A darkness swirls at the center of a world-renowned dance company, one that will engulf the artistic director, an ambitious young dancer, and a grieving psychotherapist. Some will succumb to the nightmare. Others will finally wake up.
     ...
     ```

## Usage

1. Run the Python script:

   ```
   python movie_recommendation.py
   ```

2. Enter a movie description when prompted.

3. The system will recommend the title of the most similar movie based on the given description.

